174
00:16:29,656 --> 00:16:33,159
We are both lonely and can only rely on each other

175
00:16:39,708 --> 00:16:44,003
Lina and I are both sick because of you.
Being forced to be unbearable

176
00:16:44,087 --> 00:16:47,507
That's why I lose my mind
Our mental state is not normal

177
00:16:52,011 --> 00:16:52,887
When did it start?

178
00:16:57,100 --> 00:16:58,727
-About half a year...
-One month

179
00:17:04,107 --> 00:17:08,069
Can't you just wait until I leave before starting?

180
00:17:09,320 --> 00:17:11,114
I'm still alive

181
00:17:14,200 --> 00:17:16,035
You said that the money you will receive at the beginning of the year

