The beneficiary becomes you

186
00:17:29,799 --> 00:17:31,509
What did you tell the insurance company?

187
00:17:32,886 --> 00:17:34,554
You didn't say too much, did you?

188
00:17:36,097 --> 00:17:37,515
Too talkative?

189
00:17:37,599 --> 00:17:39,434
My mom took care of everything.

190
00:17:39,517 --> 00:17:41,352
Don't ruin this.

191
00:17:41,436 --> 00:17:43,730
My mother might even be fired by the insurance company.

192
00:17:46,107 --> 00:17:48,651
It turns out you and your mother teamed up

193
00:17:49,527 --> 00:17:52,906
If I didn't have my compensation
My grandma can't live in a nursing home...

194
00:17:52,989 --> 00:17:55,450
She's just the mother of your useless mother.

195
00:17:57,076 --> 00:17:59,996
