196
00:18:00,079 --> 00:18:01,164
My grandmother only has me...

197
00:18:01,247 --> 00:18:02,123
What about me?

198
00:18:03,333 --> 00:18:07,045
You know I'm short of money.
But you abandon me so easily?

199
00:18:08,087 --> 00:18:11,549
It's the end.
Can't you think about how someone who's been abandoned feels?

200
00:18:14,385 --> 00:18:16,638
Why do you think I married you?

201
00:18:17,931 --> 00:18:20,350
The reason why I'm like you
An inconspicuous and boring woman gets married

202
00:18:20,433 --> 00:18:22,894
It's because you are stingy and save money.

203
00:18:22,977 --> 00:18:25,146
I married a woman like you who no one wants

204
00:18:25,230 --> 00:18:27,524
In the end, you repay me with hatred.

205
00:18:28,191 --> 00:18:32,320
It's all because I married you
My life has become so bad.

206
00:18:32,403 --> 00:18:35,114
