207
00:18:41,329 --> 00:18:43,540
Very bad

208
00:18:45,792 --> 00:18:48,253
You two are really terrible.

209
00:18:49,045 --> 00:18:50,547
I don't want to see you anymore

210
00:18:50,630 --> 00:18:53,508
Are you going to end our relationship with words like this?

211
00:18:53,591 --> 00:18:54,843
Of course.

212
00:18:55,885 --> 00:19:00,223
How can you trample on other people's feelings like this?

213
00:19:06,062 --> 00:19:08,022
You're still the same in the end.

214
00:19:09,482 --> 00:19:10,316
What?

215
00:19:10,400 --> 00:19:13,194
She looks like a good girl and a victim.

216
00:19:14,863 --> 00:19:19,868
Misa, you keep saying that your friends don't come to visit you.

217
00:19:19,951 --> 00:19:21,452
Not even paying for hospitalization

218
00:19:21,536 --> 00:19:24,539
You kept complaining and made me think you didn't want him anymore

219
00:19:26,708 --> 00:19:32,171
You can't make friends
I'm the only one who's always by your side, right?

220
00:19:32,589 --> 00:19:35,091
I'll go visit you and accompany you for the checkup.

221
00:19:35,174 --> 00:19:36,259
