223
00:19:38,136 --> 00:19:40,513
You just made a mistake
Do you think I'm a bad person?

224
00:19:40,597 --> 00:19:44,684
How can you do such a thing as a friend?

225
00:19:55,528 --> 00:20:00,116
My feelings towards Youya are also complicated.

226
00:20:00,909 --> 00:20:02,327
You don't know at all?

227
00:20:03,578 --> 00:20:06,414
The reason why I have always hated you...

228
00:20:09,500 --> 00:20:11,878
Anyway, it's the end, I'll tell you

229
00:20:13,212 --> 00:20:18,051
I have disliked you since I was a child

230
00:20:19,010 --> 00:20:20,845
We have never been friends

231
