-Give it to me!
-stop!

234
00:20:58,508 --> 00:21:00,259
-No!
-Give me!

235
00:21:00,343 --> 00:21:01,970
-What the hell!
-Let me go!

236
00:21:06,057 --> 00:21:09,602
Thank you for being my family

237
00:21:11,229 --> 00:21:14,190
If one day you fall in love with someone else

238
00:21:14,273 --> 00:21:17,735
Don't worry about me and remarry.

239
00:21:17,819 --> 00:21:20,530
Have you had enough of this? Damn it.

240
00:21:26,786 --> 00:21:27,662
hateful

241
00:21:34,043 --> 00:21:39,924
Lina, you have been with me since I was a child.

242
00:21:42,051 --> 00:21:46,180
