-good
-careful

254
00:23:22,026 --> 00:23:23,778
-good
-Thanks

255
00:23:23,861 --> 00:23:25,780
Bad things keep happening to me while I'm alive.

256
00:23:25,863 --> 00:23:27,240
-right
-Thank you

257
00:23:27,323 --> 00:23:30,660
There haven't been many happy moments in my life.

258
00:23:30,743 --> 00:23:34,247
But I never expected it to have such a tragic ending.

